# Type must be a resource (URI), not a literal

PREFIX dcat:    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#>
PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
PREFIX foaf:    <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>
PREFIX vcard:   <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#>

SELECT ?subject ?property ?value
WHERE {
    ?subject ?property ?value
    FILTER (!isIRI(?value))
    VALUES ?property {
        dcat:contactPoint
        dcterms:license
        dcterms:publisher
        dcterms:rights
    }
}
subjectpropertyvalue

Not using EU Publication Office Authority

 
# Not using EU Publication Office Authority

PREFIX dcat:    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#>
PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>

SELECT ?subject ?property
WHERE {
    ?subject ?property ?obj
    FILTER NOT EXISTS {
        ?subject ?property ?value
        FILTER (isIRI(?value) && STRSTARTS(STR(?value), ?taxonomy))
    }
    VALUES (?property ?taxonomy) {
        (dcat:theme         "http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/")
        (dcterms:format     "http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/file-type/")
        (dcterms:language   "http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/")
        (dcterms:accrualPeriodicity "http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/")
    }
}

        dcterms:format
        dcterms:language
        dcterms:license
        dcterms:rights
        dcterms:spatial
    }

Type of links and email adresses must be a resource (URI), not a literal

 
# Type of links and email adresses must be a resource (URI), not a literal

PREFIX dcat:    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#>
PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
PREFIX foaf:    <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>
PREFIX vcard:   <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#>

SELECT ?subject ?property ?value
WHERE {
    ?subject ?property ?value
    FILTER (!isIRI(?value))
    VALUES ?property {
        dcat:accessURL
        dcat:downloadURL
        dcat:landingPage
        foaf:homepage
        foaf:page
        vcard:hasEmail
    }
}

OK

# Catalog missing Datasets

PREFIX dcat:    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#>
PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>

SELECT ?catalog
WHERE {
    ?catalog a dcat:Catalog
    FILTER NOT EXISTS { 
        ?catalog dcat:dataset ?value
    }
}

PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>

WHERE {
    ?dataset a dcat:Dataset
    FILTER NOT EXISTS { 
        ?dataset dcat:contactPoint ?value
    }
}

Dataset missing title

 
# Dataset missing title

PREFIX dcat:    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#>
PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>

SELECT ?dataset
WHERE {
    ?dataset a dcat:Dataset
    FILTER NOT EXISTS { 
        ?dataset dcterms:title ?value
    }
}
